Galiga esc game

-PC starts at bottom center of the screen
-Screen is black (pref)
-Use arrow keys to move
-Use space to fire
-Shoot enemies
	-Circles (basic)
	-Squares (lvl 2, fast)
	-Triangles (lvl 3, fastest)
-Maybe two types of fire, reg & bomb

4 classes:
	-PC
	-CircleEnemy
	-SquareEnemy
	-TriangleEnemy

